          </li>
          <li>
            Admin can manage roles and delete users
          </li>
          <li>
            Admin can manage general tenant settings
          </li>
          <li>
            Editor can create, read, update, delete tenant-specific data
          </li>
          <li>
            Viewer can only see the tenant-specific data
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
